document.discussion_title: Orange woman weds | Central Western Daily
document.topic_text: Friends and family travelled to Queensland in June for the wedding of a former Orange woman 12 Aug 2016, 10:16 a.m. FRIENDS and family have celebrated the wedding of former Orange woman Jennifer Milton. PROUD PARENTS: Judy and Neil Milton with their daughter Jennifer on her wedding day. Photo: SUPPLIED JENNIFER Milton and Davitt Ennis were married in Mackay, Queensland on Saturday, June 25. Jennifer is the only child of Judy and Neil Milton of Orange and Davitt is the son of Gwenda and Ian Ennis of Melbourne. The bride wore a lace gown with low cut back and sequins over the straps and bodice. The bridal party also included three bridesmaids, three groomsmen and the couple’s son Kade as pageboy. The family has made its home in Mackay. Latest News
